{
  "texts": [
    "Science travels on its vocabulary.",
    "Scientific progress is impeded if words are not used consistently and effectively.",
    "It appears trivial to note that for any reasonable debate, the debaters must agree on the meaning of the words they use for debating.",
    "Yet, a closer look reveals the striking absence of consensus regarding the meaning of even the most central terms in many areas of psychology.",
    "This state of affairs inevitably produces misunderstandings and quashes hope for theoretical consensus."
  ]
}